Episode Summary   
 
A look at some of the strongest things known to mankind, such as the USS Ronald Reagan aircraft carrier elevators which lifts jets onto its deck , and a Cirque du Soleil backstage elevator which lifts the acrobats on stage. Also, the tires used on mining vehicles, a mountain bike, and the Kennedy Center&#039;s and transport vehicle for the space shuttle.
